15.1.2 Models & Diagnostics

Exploring some Generalized Linear (Mixed) model candidates:

  • Gamma (‘identity’) + AR1

❖ Model call:

```{r}
glmmTMB(formula = Time_GR ~ Condition * Stage + ar1(Stage + 0 | 
    Mouse), data = data, family = Gamma("identity"), control = glmmTMBControl(optimizer = optim, 
    optArgs = list(method = "BFGS")), REML = TRUE, start = list(beta = c(I(mean(data$Time_GR)), 
    rep(0, 19))), ziformula = ~0, dispformula = ~1)
```

❖ Performance:

performance::performance(mod)

15.1.3 Effects Analysis

Chosen model: Gamma (‘identity’) + AR1 
```{r}
glmmTMB(formula = Time_GR ~ Condition * Stage + ar1(Stage + 0 | 
    Mouse), data = data, family = Gamma("identity"), control = glmmTMBControl(optimizer = optim, 
    optArgs = list(method = "BFGS")), REML = TRUE, start = list(beta = c(I(mean(data$Time_GR)), 
    rep(0, 19))), ziformula = ~0, dispformula = ~1)
```
